Information
------------------------------

Snaketacular 
Get up close and personal with some of the creepiest creatures on earth - snakes. Host Danny Trejo and experts provide insight on home videos and real snake encounters, in this nail-biting one-hour special! 
Part of the show is dedicated to snake tourist performance shows and snake stunts. The show also features how snakes interact with other animals. For example, there is a sneak peek clip of a snake and a woodpecker attacking each other.
